_text = "I believe this is the last photo I took of my parents before they split up.\n\nIt was 2021 and I had decided to stay in Kelowna when they decided to move back to Vancouver Island. They lasted a total of 5 months without me before they broke up. I can't help but feel like my absence in their relationship caused them to realize how unhappy they were.\n\nMy mom was devastated for years after that. My dad was devastated too, but I think he recovered quicker than her. He had found someone a year later that helped him move forward in life. He began this new life with her, having three kids.\n\nIn all honesty, I do think both of my parents are better off now. But at the time it hurt. I saw my dad move on, while I was left to try and fix things with my mom.\n\nI will never blame him for finding happiness. I will just mourn the moments we had when everything was still 'normal'. \n\nI think that's why Cumberland meant so much to me."

roomInit(blackSprite, _text, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, ZachRunningMemory, ZachRunningMemory, false)
